{"Audience Type": {"selectedText": "Why and How We Collect and Store Information Sally Ride Science collects and stores some information about your daughter or son, to allow her or him to participate in some activities. For example, we store and use email addresses and other contact information to communicate with users about contests and other special events. We request parent contact information and parent consent when a girl or boy participates in Sally Ride Science events and activities. This enables us to confirm that a parent consents to their daughter's or son's participation in an event or activity and agrees to the terms of our privacy policy.", "startIndexInSegment": 0, "endIndexInSegment": 624, "value": "Children"}}
